sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Dev as DevOps Engineer
    participant DC as Data Collector
    participant ML as ML Training
    participant CTRL as Healing Controller
    participant P as Prometheus
    participant K as K8s API
    participant App as Target Pod
    participant CSV as Dataset Storage
    participant Model as Model Storage

    Note over Dev, Model: PHASE 1: Data Collection (Current)
    
    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        DC->>P: Query pod metrics (CPU, Memory)
        P-->>DC: Metrics data
        DC->>K: Get pod logs (errors, requests)
        K-->>DC: Log data
        DC->>DC: Merge & label (IsHealthy)
        DC->>CSV: Append to training_data.csv
        Note right of DC: Runs every 5 minutes
    end

    Note over Dev, Model: PHASE 2: ML Training (Planned)
    
    rect rgb(255, 250, 240)
        Dev->>ML: Trigger training job
        ML->>CSV: Load training dataset
        CSV-->>ML: Historical data (N samples)
        ML->>ML: Feature engineering
        ML->>ML: Train IsolationForest
        ML->>ML: Evaluate (precision/recall)
        ML->>Model: Save trained model.pkl
        Model-->>Dev: Training complete
    end

    Note over Dev, Model: PHASE 3: Self-Healing (Planned)
    
    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        CTRL->>Model: Load anomaly model
        Model-->>CTRL: Model loaded
        
        loop Every 30 seconds
            CTRL->>P: Query current metrics
            P-->>CTRL: CPU: 85%, Memory: 90%
            CTRL->>K: Get recent logs
            K-->>CTRL: "ERROR: Connection timeout x12"
            
            CTRL->>CTRL: Build state vector
            CTRL->>Model: Predict([0.85, 0.90, 12, ...])
            Model-->>CTRL: Anomaly detected (score: -0.45)
            
            alt Anomaly Detected
                CTRL->>CTRL: Select action (RESTART)
                CTRL->>K: DELETE Pod (app-xyz)
                K->>App: Send SIGTERM
                App-->>K: Terminated
                K-->>CTRL: New pod starting...
                CTRL->>Dev: Log healing action
            else Healthy State
                CTRL->>CTRL: Continue monitoring
            end
        end
    end

    Note over Dev, Model: System operates autonomously with human oversight
